{"meta":{"title":"停摆de思响者","subtitle":"见素抱朴，少私寡欲","description":"记录工作生活的所思所想","author":"xufeng","url":"https://webker.github.io","root":"/"},"pages":[{"title":"404 Not Found：该页无法显示","date":"2021-02-19T02:27:14.827Z","updated":"2021-02-19T02:27:14.827Z","comments":false,"path":"/404.html","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/404.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"书单","date":"2021-02-19T02:27:14.825Z","updated":"2021-02-19T02:27:14.825Z","comments":false,"path":"books/index.html","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/books/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"分类","date":"2021-02-19T02:27:14.828Z","updated":"2021-02-19T02:27:14.828Z","comments":false,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"关于我","date":"2021-03-03T10:46:17.575Z","updated":"2021-03-03T10:46:17.575Z","comments":false,"path":"about/index.html","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/about/index.html","excerpt":"","text":"常年与代码相伴，是爱好也是手艺。前后端工具使得趁手，全栈工程师一枚。 美式不加糖 酸苦是一种修行 代码不测试 那是不可能的 生活不随意 还是随性一点吧，才能处处有惊喜"},{"title":"友情链接","date":"2021-02-19T02:27:14.826Z","updated":"2021-02-19T02:27:14.826Z","comments":true,"path":"links/index.html","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/links/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"Repositories","date":"2021-02-19T02:27:14.824Z","updated":"2021-02-19T02:27:14.824Z","comments":false,"path":"repository/index.html","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/repository/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"标签","date":"2021-02-19T02:27:14.826Z","updated":"2021-02-19T02:27:14.826Z","comments":false,"path":"tags/index.html","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/tags/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"文字记录，不立 Flag","slug":"start","date":"2021-03-03T01:32:27.000Z","updated":"2021-03-03T01:32:27.000Z","comments":false,"path":"2021/03/03/start/","link":"","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/2021/03/03/start/","excerpt":"","text":"书读百遍其义自现好记性不如烂笔头 长久以来都想着提笔来记录平日的工作和生活，总是动力不足。断断续续尝试了不同的文字输出工具，经历一番折腾，最终选择使用 Hexo + Git 来搭建一个记录工具。 以往总是觉得互联网的信息随手可得，中意的内容收藏起来分分钟。但是缺少整理和思考，这些好的内容便很快消失殆尽。思考的结果如果没有留下印记，也很快会被替代。这个时候便觉得文字本身是个好东西。 文字是好，但是使用什么样的方式记录。手写？难以定位和检索。文档？整理耗时。反倒 Blog 这种“互联网”早期产物，愈久弥新。就如目前我选用的这个记录方式，借用 Git 每篇文章都可以不停的更新迭代，除了自然的时间维度，每篇文字都有它的生命周期。 某种意义上可以认为文字活了。活的文字，也许才能带来某种交流的快感，这是自我的交流，且以为始终提升的手段。 文字的内容可以是多种多样的，但是为了聚焦，还是集中在各种 Hack 的思考。工作的、生活的，问题总是接踵而至，希望花式 Hack 能够带来不一样的人生体验。 本来想立个 Flag，比如一天一篇啥的，想想还是算了，喜欢的事情自然而然就做了，反倒少了逼迫感。就权当一个检验工具吧，希望自己是真的喜欢文字。","categories":[{"name":"生活随想","slug":"生活随想","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/categories/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E9%9A%8F%E6%83%B3/"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/tags/Hexo/"},{"name":"Hack","slug":"Hack","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/tags/Hack/"}]},{"title":"Hello World","slug":"Hello-World","date":"2021-03-03T00:37:35.000Z","updated":"2021-03-03T00:37:35.000Z","comments":false,"path":"2021/03/03/Hello-World/","link":"","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/2021/03/03/Hello-World/","excerpt":"","text":"这是一个与程序代码为伍的人打招呼的最经典方式。","categories":[{"name":"程序人生","slug":"程序人生","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/categories/%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F/"}],"tags":[]}],"categories":[{"name":"生活随想","slug":"生活随想","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/categories/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E9%9A%8F%E6%83%B3/"},{"name":"程序人生","slug":"程序人生","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/categories/%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F/"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/tags/Hexo/"},{"name":"Hack","slug":"Hack","permalink":"https://webker.github.io/tags/Hack/"}]}